name: Mamba Fury 'Bruce Lee'
description: The Nike Mamba Fury ‘Bruce Lee’ delivers an alternate take on the classic Kobe 5 colorway inspired by the martial arts film star. The black textile upper is accented with a red Swoosh, its scaly texture extending up the sneaker’s side panel. Additional pops of University Red appear on the tongue, TPU heel clip and integrated lace loops. A forefoot Zoom Air unit is embedded in the foam midsole, reinforced by black and yellow rubber outsole with a snakeskin-inspired traction pattern.

name: Mamba Fury 'Snakeskin - Black Smoke Grey'
description: The Nike Mamba Fury ‘Black Smoke Grey’ applies a neutral color scheme to a low-profile hoops shoe built for speed and mobility. A reptilian texture distinguishes the textile upper, which sits atop a scaly midsole fitted with a Zoom Air unit in the forefoot. Kobe Bryant’s sheath logo adorns the tongue, heel and rubber outsole, the latter featuring a snakeskin-inspired traction pattern for enhanced grip on the hardwood.

name: Mamba Fury 'Black Racer Blue'
description: The Nike Mamba Fury ‘Black Racer Blue’ delivers a sleek colorway of a performance hoops shoe named after Kobe Bryant’s competitive spirit. The stripped-down black textile build is accented with a royal blue Swoosh on the lateral side, its surface marked with a scale pattern that extends up the quarter panel. Performance benefits include lace loops for midfoot lockdown and a TPU heel clip for rearfoot stability. Underfoot, a snakeskin-inspired traction pattern provides superior grip on the hardwood.
